StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetIRTCardListFY]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@orgID int, @fy int= null
AS BEGIN
SELECT IRTCardID, RssOrgID, DatePrepared, Sector, Frequency, ForFY, RecruiterID, RecruiterRankName, Hours, LastUpdateDate, LastUpdateUser, SectorID, CardNameDesc, 1 AS NextFyCard FROM RSSOSS.USMC.IRTCard WHERE (RssOrgID = @orgID) AND (ForFY = @fy) ORDER BY DatePrepared DESC
END
